{"tid":1577204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"914被毆手足危站控訴 921又會藍絲打人黑警放人","createTime":"2019-09-17T14:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T15:13:52.000Z","uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8e08146656acd854a301767f4f876faa20bf578d","tid":1577204,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/447574042745438/permalink/492779168224925/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F447574042745438%2Fpermalink%2F492779168224925%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5HKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=bd6d4e4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/447574042745438/permalink/492779168224925/</a><br />\n<br />\n#被打家門被淋糞  #青年危企控訴警方放生兇徒<br />\n<br />\n琴日(9月16日)有一位手足於文曲里連儂隧道頂危站，該手足為914被毆傷人士之一，其報案後，家門被人淋排泄物。<br />\n<br />\n手足被發現開始危站後，大批街坊趕到幫忙，而該手足最後亦在其他街坊護送下安全返回地面，並且沒有受傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發時該手足要求其中一名街坊為他拍下本片段並於網上發放，在其承受巨大情緒壓力下，他除了譴責警方選擇性執法外，也希望更多人能夠關注藍絲打人事件。"},{"pid":"68f2582a96d98608a57135a870a0f70f1a3c6e5c","tid":1577204,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"大家小心921啲藍絲"},{"pid":"7603019522e50950c8696a6d02002b8dfef571c9","tid":1577204,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">如果機場係春袋 商場就係紅血球<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573192\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573192</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理塞 商場篇 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563867</a><br />\n</span>全<span style=\"color: violet;\">力攪商場攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569519\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569519</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">清算黨鐵商場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1571276\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1571276</a><br />\n</span><br />\n</str